'''Aɣyul''' (illa mad as ittinin '''Aɣyyul''') iga yan ɣ imudar lli ddrnin d ufgan, ar ittaws i middn lli zdaɣnin ɣ udrar ar d ittawi ikccuḍn yawi d aman zɣ wanu.

Aɣyul iga yan umudr ɣ wanaw n wayyis, ar t ssgman mddn, yili yan wanaw yaḍen ittidiren g tagant d isaffen d tnẓruft n tfriqt d asya d imrdal nns. aɣyul yamu g wanaw n iyysan id-emm yan ikfr, yumu g winna issuḍuḍn, ig asmun n umdan aha, ar as ittasey tiɣawsiwin-nnes. ar ttinin i wmeẓẓan n uɣyul asnus.

==Tasnazɣuṛt : ==
Assaɣ n uɣyyul s tutlayt tarumit (Talatint) igat "Asinus", g tmaziɣt tlla taguri irwasn taguri ad, as tt igan d "Asnus"; Asnus g tmaziɣt igat umẓẓay n uɣyyul nɣ iwis n uɣyyul.

